      <title>美元回落致股市结束五日跌势：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者终于被诱导买入美国股票。在经历了五天的下跌，股价缩水超过一万亿美元之后，华尔街结束了自四月份以来最长的股市下跌周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 22:26:22 GMT</pubDate>
